{"title":"Save 20% on Cycling Gear During the 2025 REI Member Moment Sale","link":"https://bikerumor.com/save-20-on-cycling-gear-2025-rei-member-moment-sale/","date":1741957200000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/REI-member-moment-cycling-sale-Kingman-800x534.jpeg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" alt=\"(Photo/REI Co-op)\" /></p>\n<p>Great news, REI Members: from March 14-24 members can utilize an exclusive coupon code to save 20% on one full-price item and one REI Outlet item. Unlike most sales, this discount can be applied to almost any full-price item (<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fpromotions%2Fcoupons\" target=\"_blank\">some exclusions apply</a>), which means it’s a great time to commit to that big purchase you’ve had your eye on. Use the coupon code “MEMBER2025” at checkout to take advantage of this perk. For even more savings, REI Co-op Members can use coupon code “USED2025” to save 20% on one Re/Supply item.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out some of the new gear you won’t want to miss out on any items eligible for purchase with your REI Co-op member coupon.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com\" target=\"_blank\">Shop New Arrivals at REI</a>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fs%2Fcycling-new-arrivals\" target=\"_blank\">Shop New Cycling Gear at REI</a>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/REI-member-moment-sale-Kingman.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/REI-member-moment-sale-Kingman.jpeg\" alt=\"REI member moment sale Kingman\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/REI-member-moment-sale-Kingman.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/REI-member-moment-sale-Kingman-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/REI-member-moment-sale-Kingman-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/REI-member-moment-sale-Kingman-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/REI-member-moment-sale-Kingman-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/REI-member-moment-sale-Kingman-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo/REI Co-op)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>REI Member Benefits</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to this one-time discount, REI rewards its loyal customers with exclusive deals, early access to limited-edition items, and expert advice from its staff of passionate outdoor enthusiasts. Most bikes purchased at REI come with coast-to-coast support, which includes one year of free adjustments, in-store bike assembly, and access to bike experts at more than 170 bike shops. The perks are even better for REI Co-op Members: 20% off shop services and free Co-op Cycles brand tubes with the purchase of a flat tire repair.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, members can save even more when they sign up for the REI Co-op Mastercard, (for full terms and conditions, visit <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fmembership%2Fmastercard%2Fpreapproval\">REI.com/mastercard</a>) earning 15% in total REI Rewards. That includes the annual 10% Co-op Member Reward on eligible full-price purchases, plus 5% on eligible purchases at REI with your REI Co-op Mastercard.<br /><br />If you’re not already an REI Co-op Member, you can <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fmembership\">sign up now</a> and enjoy the 20% member coupon.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Coupon-Eligible Bike Gear &amp; Apparel</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F245021\">Smith Forefront 3 Mips Bike Helmet</a>: $270</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Smith-forefront-3-helmets.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"782\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Smith-forefront-3-helmets.webp\" alt=\"Smith forefront 3 helmets\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Smith-forefront-3-helmets.webp 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Smith-forefront-3-helmets-297x145.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Smith-forefront-3-helmets-1536x751.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Smith-forefront-3-helmets-120x59.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Smith-forefront-3-helmets-768x375.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Protect your dome with the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/redesigned-smith-forefront-3-helmet-boa-hardline-full-face/\" target=\"_blank\">all-new Smith Forefront 3 Mountain Bike Helmet</a>. This new version of the popular design features an internal injected roll cage, extended back coverage, and a Mips Safety System integrated into its padding. Enjoy a 25% increase in airflow with 20 vents plus AirEvac ventilation to ride comfortably in a range of conditions. For even more customization, easily dial the fit with the BOA Fit System and adjust the visor to stash goggles or secure sunglasses in the shell.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F245021\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F245812%2Fstio-shifter-bike-shirt-mens\">Stio Shifter Bike Shirt — Men’s</a>: $99</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Stio-Shifter-Bike-Shirt.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Stio-Shifter-Bike-Shirt.webp\" alt=\"Stio Shifter Bike Shirt\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Stio-Shifter-Bike-Shirt.webp 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Stio-Shifter-Bike-Shirt-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Stio-Shifter-Bike-Shirt-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Stio-Shifter-Bike-Shirt-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Stio-Shifter-Bike-Shirt-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Stio-Shifter-Bike-Shirt-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Stio-Shifter-Bike-Shirt-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This breezy shirt has a relaxed fit that won’t interfere with your flow. It’s made from a moisture-wicking fabric to move sweat away from your body during tough climbs or scorching heat on the singletrack.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F245812%2Fstio-shifter-bike-shirt-mens\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F194054%2Fwild-rye-galena-gel-bike-gloves-womens\">Wild Rye Galena Gel Bike Gloves</a>: $40</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/WIld-Rye-Galena-Gel-Bike-Gloves.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/WIld-Rye-Galena-Gel-Bike-Gloves.webp\" alt=\"WIld Rye Galena Gel Bike Gloves\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/WIld-Rye-Galena-Gel-Bike-Gloves.webp 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/WIld-Rye-Galena-Gel-Bike-Gloves-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/WIld-Rye-Galena-Gel-Bike-Gloves-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/WIld-Rye-Galena-Gel-Bike-Gloves-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/WIld-Rye-Galena-Gel-Bike-Gloves-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/WIld-Rye-Galena-Gel-Bike-Gloves-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/WIld-Rye-Galena-Gel-Bike-Gloves-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These gel bike gloves are made with a wicking, four-way stretch shell and feature a gel-padded palm for comfort. Softer details, like the touch-screen-friendly fingertips and cotton thumbs for wiping your face, add ride-ready functionality.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F194054%2Fwild-rye-galena-gel-bike-gloves-womens\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Rapha Core Rain Jackets — <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F243302%2Frapha-core-rain-jacket-mens\">Men’s</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F243303%2Frapha-core-rain-jacket-iii-womens\">Women’s</a>:$190</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rapha-Core-Rain-Jackets.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rapha-Core-Rain-Jackets.webp\" alt=\"Rapha Core Rain Jackets\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rapha-Core-Rain-Jackets.webp 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rapha-Core-Rain-Jackets-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rapha-Core-Rain-Jackets-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rapha-Core-Rain-Jackets-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rapha-Core-Rain-Jackets-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rapha-Core-Rain-Jackets-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rapha-Core-Rain-Jackets-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Lightweight, wind-resistant, and fully waterproof, the Rapha Core Rain Jacket will keep you protected from the elements on your ride. The design features a two-way AquaGuard zipper to allow you to dump heat and take in fresh air. Reflective details add visibility during inclement conditions. When not in use, the jacket packs down small enough to tuck into a jersey pocket.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F243302%2Frapha-core-rain-jacket-mens\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Men’s</a>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F243303%2Frapha-core-rain-jacket-iii-womens\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Women’s</a>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F247160%2Fblackburn-chamber-tubeless-floor-pump\">Blackburn Chamber Tubeless Floor Pump</a>: $200</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blackburn-Chamber-Tubeless-Floor-Pump.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blackburn-Chamber-Tubeless-Floor-Pump.webp\" alt=\"Blackburn Chamber Tubeless Floor Pump\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blackburn-Chamber-Tubeless-Floor-Pump.webp 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blackburn-Chamber-Tubeless-Floor-Pump-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blackburn-Chamber-Tubeless-Floor-Pump-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blackburn-Chamber-Tubeless-Floor-Pump-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blackburn-Chamber-Tubeless-Floor-Pump-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blackburn-Chamber-Tubeless-Floor-Pump-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blackburn-Chamber-Tubeless-Floor-Pump-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Blackburn Chamber tubeless floor pump is an alternative to the compressors and hoses filling your garage. It works by charging up a burst of pressured air that then releases into the tire to seat the bead and then proceeds to pump it up as you would any other tire. You can tweak the pressure through an air bleed button on the pump.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The pump’s handle is a riser bar with comfy grips — but the 31.8 mm stem means you can swap that for an old favorite set of handlebars if you want.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F247160%2Fblackburn-chamber-tubeless-floor-pump\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F238299%2Fpanaracer-gravelking-r-tire\">Panaracer GravelKing R Tire</a>: $80</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Panaracer-GravelKing-R-Tire.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"953\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Panaracer-GravelKing-R-Tire.webp\" alt=\"Panaracer GravelKing R Tire\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Panaracer-GravelKing-R-Tire.webp 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Panaracer-GravelKing-R-Tire-297x177.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Panaracer-GravelKing-R-Tire-1536x915.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Panaracer-GravelKing-R-Tire-120x71.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Panaracer-GravelKing-R-Tire-768x457.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Crafted with a lightweight yet supple protective casing with Panaracer’s TuffTex R technology, the GravelKing R tire provides a fast and smooth ride over gravel, dirt, and rough pavement. A Zero Slip Grip compound contributes additional gravel prowess and offers high resilience against temperature variance for consistent performance. The brand’s newly redesigned BeadLock accommodates several rim types, including hookless and hooked clincher styles. Available in tubeless designs (700c x 30 mm and wider) and a 700c x 28 mm non-tubeless-compatible option.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F238299%2Fpanaracer-gravelking-r-tire\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F245133%2Flezyne-micro-drive-800-and-strip-drive-300-bike-light-set\">Lezyne Micro Drive 800+ and Strip Drive 300+ Bike Light Set</a>: $95</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lezyne-Micro-Drive-800-and-Strip-Drive-300-Bike-Light-Set.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lezyne-Micro-Drive-800-and-Strip-Drive-300-Bike-Light-Set.webp\" alt=\"Lezyne Micro Drive 800+ and Strip Drive 300+ Bike Light Set\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lezyne-Micro-Drive-800-and-Strip-Drive-300-Bike-Light-Set.webp 1600w, ht